title: JG Main Looking For a Team T4 or T3
body:
Hi. I'm looking for a clash team who needs a jungle main. Currently I'm Silver 2, but I've only played like 14 ranked games this season.  I ended last season/pre season at high Gold (gold 1 or gold 2). I have a pretty flexible pool, am good natured and a team player. If need be, I could fill support as it is my secondary role. 

IGN: Theoccio
Add me if you have any questions or think I might be a good fit.
